{"tid":1600849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】我真係好憎你哋燒國旗","createTime":"2019-09-28T18:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:45:04.000Z","uid":255970,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a553dae85813de078215b061ad4b50225a21326","tid":1600849,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:31:12.000Z","msg":"傻啦，我不知幾贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。題目係有誤導，但確實係想講燒旗呢回事。<br />\n<br />\n3個幾月以嚟，抗爭者得到全世界嘅讚許，係因為運動有質素，具針對性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，絕不禍及無辜。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">燒旗亦應該發揮「針對性」，所以我提議：只燒大星&mdash;&mdash;中共</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。無論係大中華膠、自決派、港獨派或者城邦派，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗中共都必定係最大公因數。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外媒亦好清楚中國係中國，中共係中共，例如The Economist 前幾日就寫到：Those protests were a stunning vote of no confidence in China&rsquo;s Communist-controlled legal system [1]，而例子多不勝數，不贅。外媒絕對會明白「燒大星」當中所以然。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>總括嚟講，燒大星有幾個好處：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 向國際社會鄭重表明：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港逆權運動是抵抗中共及其極權管治</span></span></strong>，而非針對中國土地上的農民、工人、城市小資產階級和民族資產階級（即其餘四星）[2]<br />\n<br />\n2. 對中共喉舌及建制派宣傳機器造成論述及編採困難：起碼令他們不能再動輒指控抗爭者「反中亂港」，因為我們是反共；他們要將反共連繫到反中，也需花一番論述功夫。同時，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他們即使要播燒旗畫面，都只可播大星被燒毀</span></span></strong>，智力正常的大陸人目睹這一幕，都必定心領神會；此舉也或多或少，可與一些不滿中共的大陸普通百姓建立起無形的連結，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這也是中共最忌諱的「意識型態輸出」</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3. 外媒漸漸將今次逆權運動的焦點放在「香港市民反警暴」之上。抗爭者手段上多元，但議題上卻單元，難以吸引更多國際曝光。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨近十一國殤，燒大星更別具「賀佢老母」的意義</span></span></strong>，也可給外媒一個較為清新（傳媒極為看重事件新鮮與否）、另類的畫面，留住他們的目光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警亂咁嚟，就向警總掟蛋、向地區警署掟磚；<br />\n黨鐵配合黑警濫捕，就跳閘、打爛入閘機；<br />\n福建幫call人抗爭者，就杯葛富臨、優品360；<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共河水犯井水，就燒中共嗰粒大星，合情合理。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">方法：</span></strong><br />\n買五星旗有咁大得咁大，唔怕燒唔到，最怕外媒睇唔到。至於點樣集中燒一粒星？可以先淋濕或噴濕大星以外嘅旗身，又或者用打邊爐火槍燒撚爛佢。相信其他CHING會發掘出更多方法，燒得更壯觀、壯烈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，或者會有CHING提出，咁點解唔直接燒中共黨旗？因為燒黨旗嘅針對性 冇燒大星咁高。有無辜嘅四星喺隔離，而偏要燒大星，先顯得大星係幾撚乞人憎，亦反映出不傷無辜嘅原則。當然，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">燒黨旗亦唔係壞事，小弟亦絕對贊成</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n十月一號，賀佢老母。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命；煲底相見，一言為定。</span></strong></span>（有返少少盼望，個人先冇咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n [1]<br />\n The Economist  / Sep 26th：Over the past four months as many as 2m Hong Kongers&mdash;or more than a quarter of the city&rsquo;s residents&mdash;have marched to demand the scrapping of a bill that would have exposed criminal suspects to the mainland&rsquo;s courts. Those protests were a stunning vote of no confidence in China&rsquo;s Communist-controlled legal system. They worked: the extradition bill is being withdrawn.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.economist.com/china/2019/09/26/chinas-demand-for-undivided-loyalty-is-causing-tragedy-in-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3fMDIWAI4Ln34SH9texljY18xIFdfhiuxT5dHFYV6uo6Ok-wvZ1u6PYR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fchina%2F2019%2F09%2F26%2Fchinas-demand-for-undivided-loyalty-is-causing-tragedy-in-hong-kong%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3fMDIWAI4Ln34SH9texljY18xIFdfhiuxT5dHFYV6uo6Ok-wvZ1u6PYR8&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rxx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=589597fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.economist.com/china/2019/09/26/chinas-demand-for-undivided-loyalty-is-causing-tragedy-in-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR3fMDIWAI4Ln34SH9texljY18xIFdfhiuxT5dHFYV6uo6Ok-wvZ1u6PYR8</a><br />\n<br />\n[2]<br />\n可能你會話嗰班「城市小資產階級」同埋「民族資產階級」亦係敵人，但起碼農民、工人呢兩個受壓逼嘅兩群人唔係先。"},{"pid":"49a384a142c762d09bc6504eec45cbbde7002b96","tid":1600849,"uid":197393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:32:46.000Z","msg":"贊成咁又點呀<br />\n屌你老母標題黨"},{"pid":"aed5aed80ab7fae147a3c2cde7445ef37d52ad6c","tid":1600849,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:33:21.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"515d6890b444c2089eec98b29befbf719368a1ec","tid":1600849,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:35:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"916331584dccd4c8ed96fe44ef0ca6ab46c3d802","tid":1600849,"uid":35953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:36:56.000Z","msg":"負評係比你個標題嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f9b9ab3dec0730eecd42113585e097ba975307","tid":1600849,"uid":205378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:37:43.000Z","msg":"咁不如索性燒黨旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d67bf192d2197410bb7def819c8347037eccf1d","tid":1600849,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:38:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"d80b6dfd7